    • Method Detail

      • onGSResponse

        void onGSResponse(java.lang.String method,
                GSResponse response,
                java.lang.Object context)
        This method will be invoked after the Gigya server completes to process your request. The method receives Gigya's response and should handle it.
        Parameters:
        method - the name of the Gigya API method that was requested.
        response - Gigya's response.
        context - the context object passed by the application as a parameter to the API method, or null if no context object has been passed.
